# Liabilities Insurance Premium Liabilities Gross Accounting Amount

## identifier
de8846

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the gross premium liabilities, calculated as UPL - DAC, where 

UPL = Unearned Premium Liability as determined in accordance with the relevant accounting standards.

DAC = Deferred Acquisition Costs as determined in accordance with the relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.PremiumLiabilitiesGrossAccounting.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.05
- period=instant
